data.description: Call your favorite realtor and come visit this SouthSide property located in a quiet cul-de-sac in an established neighborhood. This two-story home features the primary bedroom downstairs, barn-door accents your primary bathroom, additional half-bath located downstairs ideal for guest use, with two bedrooms, full bath, and an additional living area upstairs. Additional living space can be used as an office, a work-out area, game-room, theater room, choice is yours! This home has a large back-yard with a deck for all your back-yard gatherings! With a reasonable offer Seller is willing to negotiate roof.  Don't wait, book your tour today! More pictures coming SOON!
